lead_paragraph: Sophie Brunner scored 16 points with seven rebounds, five assists and four steals as a balanced, 17th-ranked Arizona State built an early lead and held off No. 19 California 57-49 in a Pac-12 Conference opener Saturday night.

headline.print_headline: No. 17 Arizona State Women Defeat No. 19 Cal 57-49 in Pac-12
